uth-West region, has come with positive result. February 24, 2020 In "News" Lagos—Lagos State House of Assembly, on Thursday, committed the Bill for a Law to establish the State Security outfit, “Amotekun” Corps, 2020 to the House Committee on Information, Publicity, Security and Strategy and report back to the House sine die. February 21, 2020 In "News" ...Set for public hearing Monday By Ebunoluwa Sessou The Lagos State House of Assembly has lent its voice to the South West Security outfit, Amotekun and has fixed a public hearing on the outfit for Monday 24th February 2020. Speaker of the House, Mr. Mudashiru Obasa subsequently committed the Bill… February 20, 2020 In "News"